+#!/usr/bin/env python3
+"filter for aistrategy.csv"
+
+import csv
+import sys
+
+REMOVE_COLUMNS = [
+    'record_created',
+    'record_modified',
+    'user_modified',
+    'owner_org',
+    'owner_org_title',
+]
+
+
+def main():
+    reader = csv.DictReader(sys.stdin)
+    outnames = [f for f in reader.fieldnames if f not in REMOVE_COLUMNS]
+    writer = csv.DictWriter(sys.stdout, outnames)
+    writer.writeheader()
+    for row in reader:
+        try:
+            for rem in REMOVE_COLUMNS:
+                del row[rem]
+            writer.writerow(row)
+        except ValueError:
+            pass
+
+
+main()
